post_title: FS: T206 Ed Hahn P150 PSA 6
post_content:
Hi all,

I have a PSA 6 Ed Hahn P150 for sale for $800.  Hahn is one of the more difficult PSA 6+ cards with 47 cards graded at that level or higher (not including SGC).  Hahn was the lead off batter for the 1906 World Series champions (hitless wonders).  If you’d like to make an offer, feel free to shoot me a DM.

-Paul
Hey Paul- LMK if your interested in trading. Thanks.
